27257025-82aa-487c-bbc2-0641667d83d3.title: Note
27257025-82aa-487c-bbc2-0641667d83d3.text: Do you have the book Jethick gives you?

e1442261-5167-4e82-8669-cace2d77ad44.title: Jethick
e1442261-5167-4e82-8669-cace2d77ad44.text:
Hello, I don't recognise you. We don't get many
newcomers around here.

f5d70703-8640-4675-8cc7-2077bc0b0885.title: Jethick
f5d70703-8640-4675-8cc7-2077bc0b0885.text:
The plague of course. Not many people want to come
to a place like this and the few that do normally get
stopped by the mourners.

98985706-c6e4-455a-9868-90b6f95358e5.title: Jethick
98985706-c6e4-455a-9868-90b6f95358e5.text:
All you'll find here now are the dead and the dying.
Even our own king has abandoned us.

639d8faf-c47c-4e33-9b6d-1ec0ee04a38b.title: Jethick
639d8faf-c47c-4e33-9b6d-1ec0ee04a38b.text:
Yes, King Tyras of West Ardougne. He's the brother
of King Lathas, the ruler of East Ardougne.

0959f889-40de-4790-9fcf-631c0470ff2d.title: Jethick
0959f889-40de-4790-9fcf-631c0470ff2d.text:
Well he's always been a bit of an explorer. He's led
multiple expeditions into the uncharted lands to the west.

7be99412-0acc-428e-a153-26c3133e1916.title: Jethick
7be99412-0acc-428e-a153-26c3133e1916.text:
The plague first started when he came back from one
of these expeditions. More than a few suspect that some
of his men caught it out there and brought it back with
them.

fe7ff7aa-833c-406d-ac8a-62f5359b84fa.title: Jethick
fe7ff7aa-833c-406d-ac8a-62f5359b84fa.text:
The king didn't care though. He just left on another
expedition to the west. He hasn't been seen since. He
left the city warder Bravek in charge but he's no
better.

87a22c73-cb96-4b61-ae0b-604358fe3b0f.title: Jethick
87a22c73-cb96-4b61-ae0b-604358fe3b0f.text:
Anyway, you clearly didn't come here to talk about
kings. So tell me, what brings you to West Ardougne?

3fdaea40-2211-4ebe-a1b7-445d9fdc88df.title: <player>
3fdaea40-2211-4ebe-a1b7-445d9fdc88df.text:
I'm looking for a woman from East Ardougne called
Elena.

b2f87f27-fd6c-4ac5-b713-a96f84ddc32b.title: Jethick
b2f87f27-fd6c-4ac5-b713-a96f84ddc32b.text:
East Ardougnian women are easier to find in East
Ardougne. Not many would come to West Ardougne to
find one. Although the name is familiar, what does she
look like?

a6702a48-cb0e-4f62-a871-3ac7a999cd6d.title: <player>
a6702a48-cb0e-4f62-a871-3ac7a999cd6d.text: Um... brown hair... in her twenties...

6ba8b0d2-1f08-4ccd-85a5-df974240510e.title: Jethick
6ba8b0d2-1f08-4ccd-85a5-df974240510e.text:
Hmmm, that doesn't narrow it down a huge amount...
I'll need to know more than that, or see a picture?

39765f77-5e46-4d28-8b54-48961061e508.title: Note
39765f77-5e46-4d28-8b54-48961061e508.text:
get portrait,
step can be skipped if player already
has the portrait on them.

79124c35-3c78-4087-ae30-8b95f40d188d.title: Jethick
79124c35-3c78-4087-ae30-8b95f40d188d.text:
Hello, I don't recognise you. We don't get many
newcomers around here.

1d5be935-428f-4b67-8ad7-d5521635da31.title: Jethick
1d5be935-428f-4b67-8ad7-d5521635da31.text:
Ah yes. She came over here to help the plague victims.
I think she is staying over with the Rehnison family.

61f96f13-b683-443c-99e6-d2400af14e6a.title: Jethick
61f96f13-b683-443c-99e6-d2400af14e6a.text:
They live in the small timbered building at the far north
side of town. I've not seen her around here in a while,
mind.

df96ba1b-dc9c-4ca5-94ee-ac4b7e5fa6b3.title: Jethick
df96ba1b-dc9c-4ca5-94ee-ac4b7e5fa6b3.text:
I don't suppose you could run me a little errand while
you're over there? I borrowed this book from them, can
you return it?

options.text: Yes, I'll return it for you.
No, I don't have time for that.

c7cf97e6-d8e7-4e32-b903-cca751697c3d.title: <player>
c7cf97e6-d8e7-4e32-b903-cca751697c3d.text: No, I don't have time for that.

143f412b-0fa5-4dc2-82d8-cc89c3f2bb31.title: <player>
143f412b-0fa5-4dc2-82d8-cc89c3f2bb31.text: Yes, I'll return it for you.

20536fa6-d3ad-4629-a26d-7182003815b9.title: Jethick
20536fa6-d3ad-4629-a26d-7182003815b9.text: Hello. We don't get many newcomers around here.

96caee5d-ed56-477f-8dd3-81fedec504fb.title: Jethick
96caee5d-ed56-477f-8dd3-81fedec504fb.text:
I'm surprised you're still here. Not many like to stick
around this place if they have the choice.
